
<%= @tweet.content %> <br><br>

To edit your tweet, just click this link. <br>
<a href="/tweets/<%= @tweet.id %>/edit">Edit Tweet</a><br><br>


To delete your tweet, just fill out the form below. <br>
<form action="/tweets/<%= @tweet.id %>/delete" method="post">
  <input type="hidden" id="hidden" name="_method" value="delete">
  <input type="submit" value="Delete Tweet">

</form>